  "slug": "what-does-my-guilt-about-this-say-about-my-worthiness-story",
  "title": "What Does My Guilt About This Say About My Worthiness Story?",
  "subtitle": "A journal prompt set for unpacking the guilt that comes with unearned money",
  "excerpt": "A journal prompt set for examining the guilt that arrives with an inheritance, a gift, or a windfall. Works through what the guilt is protecting, where the earning rule came from, and what keeping the money without guilt would actually mean.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Written for homemade.education.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal set for the guilt that arrives with money that wasn't earned. Inheritance, a gift from someone who had more, a legal settlement, a win, the common thread is that the usual transaction (effort for payment) didn't happen. These prompts work through what the guilt is doing and where it came from.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journal practice? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What is my relationship with this money right now?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Describe in plain terms. Is it in your account? Are you avoiding looking at it? Have you already begun to spend it away?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What feeling comes up most when I think about keeping it?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Name the feeling without explaining it. Guilt, discomfort, relief, grief, write whichever is there.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where did I learn that money only counts if I earned it?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Was there a person who said this? A household rule? Something you absorbed without being told?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What does the guilt say I should do with this money?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write the instruction the guilt is giving you. Give it away, spend it quickly, donate most of it, hold it loosely. What does it want you to do?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "If this money were an amount I had earned, what would I do with it?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Notice whether the answer is different from what you're actually doing. The gap is the belief in action.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
